### Test 1 — List and seed data
GET http://localhost:8000/api/books
Expected: 200, three books from the database

### Test 1b — Get single book
GET http://localhost:8000/api/books/1

### Test 2a — Search (q=clean)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/books?q=clean
Expected: 200, only "Clean Code"

### Test 2b — Search (limit=2)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/books?limit=2
Expected: 200, first two rows

### Test 3 — Create new book
POST http://localhost:8000/api/books
Content-Type: application/json

{ "title":"Refactoring", "author":"Martin Fowler", "year":2018 }
Expected: 201 Created, Location: /api/books/4

### Test 4a — Partial update (genre only)
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/books/1
Content-Type: application/json

{ "genre": "Software Craftsmanship" }
Expected: 200

### Test 4b — Delete a book
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/books/2
Expected: 200

### Test 5 — Verify book exists after retrieval
GET http://localhost:8000/api/books/1

### Part F — SQL Injection Attempt 1 (OR injection on id)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/books/1%20OR%201=1
Expected: 404 (should not find book with ID "1 OR 1=1")

### Part F — SQL Injection Attempt 2 (quote escape in q parameter)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/books?q='%20OR%20'1'='1
Expected: 200, but empty data array
